Package: spliceTerrain
Type: Package
Title: Sashimi-Style RNA-seq Coverage and Junction Visualisation
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        "Lachlan", "Baer",
        email = "baerlachlan@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5213-3401")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools to visualise RNA sequencing alignments as
    sashimi-style plots showing read coverage and splice junction usage
    across genomic regions. Alignments from BAM files are summarised into
    coverage tracks and junction arcs, which can be displayed alongside
    transcript annotations. The package provides utilities for mapping
    genomic coordinates to plot space, compressing intronic regions, and
    visualising local splicing variation across samples.
